# 14. Luồng tổng hợp cuối cùng

```text
Customer gửi message đầu tiên
        ↓
Conversation Service
        ↓
Postgres transaction:
  create conversation WAITING
  create first message
  create outbox event
        ↓
Outbox Publisher
        ↓
Kafka: ConversationCreated
        ↓
Routing Service
        ↓
Agent Service
        ↓
Redis atomic reserve agent
        ↓
 ┌─────────────────────────────┐
 │ Có agent                     │
 │ - reserve agent              │
 │ - update conversation         │
 │ - confirm reservation         │
 │ - publish ConversationAssigned│
 └─────────────────────────────┘

 hoặc

 ┌─────────────────────────────┐
 │ Không có agent               │
 │ - push conversation_id queue  │
 │ - keep status WAITING         │
 │ - publish ConversationQueued  │
 └─────────────────────────────┘
```

