# 15. Khi nào nên scale từng phần?

## Scale Conversation Service

Khi:

```text
nhiều message
nhiều conversation create/update
DB write load cao
```

Scale bằng:

```text
horizontal service instances
Postgres read replica
partition messages by created_at/conversation_id
```

## Scale Routing Service

Khi:

```text
nhiều event ConversationCreated
nhiều queue
logic routing phức tạp
```

Scale bằng:

```text
Kafka consumer group
Redis atomic lock theo conversation_id
partition queue theo skill/team
```

## Scale Agent Service

Khi:

```text
nhiều agent state update
nhiều reserve/release
```

Scale bằng:

```text
stateless instances
Redis Cluster
Lua script atomic
```

## Scale Redis

Dùng:

```text
Redis Sentinel hoặc Redis Cluster
replica
AOF persistence
monitor memory
```

